name: I Walk Among Zombies Vol. 3
summary: Gunfire rings out, shattering the safe haven of the town hall. Violent death. People driven to suicide. A mystery group behind the scenes. An imminent horde of zombies. And the intelligent zombies are finally on the move. What will become of Yuusuke and the others?

name: I Wanna Play That Picture Puzzle with Numbers All Day!
summary:
I want to play that puzzle—where you look at the numbers on the left and top and fill in the intersecting squares—forever!

In a rainy café, you can quietly and endlessly immerse yourself in solving puzzles.

name: I Won't Forget Hue
summary: Disorganized and alone, a woman finds herself crafting new glasses in order to look at her own home with different shaded views. I won't forget Hue is a psychedelic thriller experience. You'll go searching for new lenses, try to figure out what is happening to her home and why she is all alone.

name: I Want to Go for a Walk
summary:
I like going for walks.

I use them to sort through my thoughts, to try to make sense of them, but lately that hasn't seemed to help as much.

name: I Want an Identity
I Want to Die: Remake
I Will Escape
summary: You are Brian Lowfield, you awaken on the cold floor of a prison cell with no recollection of what happened in the past 24 hours. You've lost your memory and you're completely stripped from your gear. On the floor, you find a picture of a young girl. You don't know who she is, yet she looks familiar to you. You have no idea what's going on, but one thought strongly resounds in your mind: I Will Escape!

name: Iwaihime: Matsuri
summary:
A port of the visual novel Iwaihime from PC to Playstation 4 and Vita.
It will include new scenarios.

name: I will eat you
summary: I will eat you! Run, hide, shout and try to survive in the game, full of fun and funny moments. Play with random players or with friends. But whatever you do, DO NOT ENTER THE DEN OF THE BEAST!

name: I Will Never Fall for My Tsundere Classmate, so I Will Just Date a Background Character Instead!
summary: A short parody visual novel about romance with a tsundere girl... Or not?

name: I Will Return
I wa Sanjutsu Nari
summary: One of the first hospital management games. You hire staff, expand your hospital and advertise your services. But also take decisions on salary and how much medicine you prescribe to your patients. At times are prompted with text scenarios and have to decide how to handle them. It might be Yakuzas raiding the hospital, competing hospitals opening up, embezzling scandals etc.

name: I Want to Run Away From My Goth Mommy... or Do I?
summary: You dashed into the first apartment you could find, trying to escape the sudden downpour—and here's the result: a slamming door, an unfamiliar interior, and… her.

name: I Was a Teenage Exocolonist
summary: Spend your teenage years on an alien planet in this narrative life sim with card-based battles. Explore, grow up, and fall in love. The choices you make and skills you master over ten years will determine the course of your life and the survival of your colony.

name: I Will Purify You
summary: I Will Purify You (I.P.U.) is a 2D pixel side-scroll action game where you play as James, an exorcist of the Hunter Union. Battle countless Anomalies and purify powerful, alluring female bosses to restore peace to a world consumed by chaos.

name: I Wanna Make a Dragon Game
summary: A short visual novel made in under 24 hours.

name: I Wish I Were the Moon
summary: A game about a boy-girl-moon love triangle by Daniel Benmergui, in which the player attempts to find all the possible outcomes of the scenario. (Inspired by Italo Calvino's 'The Distance of the Moon'.)

name: I Wanna Be A Game Dev!
summary: Live out your school days as you navigate the rocky world of game development! Can you make an amazing game, or will something get in the way?

name: I Wish it Was Morning All the Time
summary: I Wish it Was Morning All the Time is a novel game released in 2021. It was first announced as a form that could be played with browser games and downloads. It was later ported to Steam.

name: IWL: Interstellar Wrestling League - 011: Character - Uber Tuber
Iwaihime
summary: From hit writer Ryukishi07, the creator of When They Cry, comes a story on the theme of “curses.” Strike down the dark riddle of dolls and soot in this supernatural horror visual novel.

name: I Wanna Kill The Kamilia 2
summary: I Wanna Kill The Kamilia 2 is an I Wanna Be The Guy fangame made by Influcca and it is the second entry of the medley game series "Kill The Kamilia". This is a sequel/remake to I Wanna Kill The Kamilia, a game originally made by oyo. Your mission is to, once again, defeat The Kamilia, but this time the challenges are much tougher and the stage remixes are much better refined.

name: iWarehouse: World Tour
summary:
Can you explore and break down the puzzle world? Well then, get stocking for a tour.
iWarehouse is one of the best adventure puzzle game on the app store which will surely test your problem solving abilities.

name: Iwai Keitai Kaitsuu! Tamagotchi Plus
summary: The Keitai Kaitsuu Tamagotchi Plus, usually shortened to the Keitai or K-Tama, is a Tamagotchi released in Japan on November 23, 2004. It builds on the Tamagotchi Plus, while adding new features, such as cell phone capabilities and a money system.

name: I Wanna Be The Guy Remastered
summary: This is a faithful remaster of the original I Wanna Be The Guy, aiming to balance the spirit of the original game with the desire for consistent physics like the fangames that came after while fixing some of the jank.

name: I Was Always Filled With Anger
summary: A game poem

name: I Wanna Be The ROM Hack: Prototype
IWL: Interstellar Wrestling League - 087: Character - Mandible
I Won’t Let You Level up in My Goblin Town
summary: Interfere in a turn based fight! When adventurers come to your goblin town to level up, your strongest warrior goblin meets them in Active Time Battle. Run around town gathering the equipment and potions he needs to defeat any adventurer party.

name: I Want to Talk About My Friend
summary: "I Want To Talk About My Friend" is a horror game based on ancient folklore, but it's also a tribute to some friends gone too soon.

name: I woke up in the house of a fat man: he's over 30 years old and loves beer and games
summary: Escape your beer-fuelled future. After waking up in an unfamiliar place with a pounding headache, you realise that you have become a prisoner of Alfaskuf. Your future is a never-ending game of tanks and beer madness. To escape, you must challenge the master of this gloomy labyrinth.

name: I Was Lost
summary: Move walls, avoid danger in a labyrinthic poem, and create your own stories in this unique puzzle experience where each level is a poem's verse unraveling as you progress. Control not only your position but also move walls to create new paths and escape from seemingly impossible situations.

name: I Wanna Win!
summary: Do you like to win? Then, this game is for you! Win 25 various levels which require thinking, accuracy, speed, attention, and be the best!

name: I Will Make You Scared of This Red Box.
summary: The Red Cube wants to eat all of the pills in the hospital. The problem is that he has already had WAY too many! You need to collect all of the the pills in the facility so that he doesn't eat any more. Be careful though...The Cube REALLY likes his pills...

name: I Want to Drive That Van
summary: Have you ever looked at that broken down camper van in some of the human settlements and thought "it'd be cool if I could drive this"? No? Well I did, and now this is here.

name: I Want Out!
summary: A short and retro style 'escape the room' game.

name: I Wanna Escape Into My Mind
summary:
A game about change, identity and figuring out who you are.

Take the role of the kid as you enter a fortress that lets you enter your own mind. It'll take a lot of strength and willpower to get to the center of the fortress. Will you enter your own mind or will you perish? Or will you do something entirely different?

name: I Wanna Ascend
summary: As you climb this place, you will fall countless times, sinking into despair. Prove that you're not just a loudmouth coward—reach the top. The 2D platforming jump game that will break your keyboard: I Wanna Ascend.

name: Iwakutsugi
summary: This is the third horror adventure game from TEAM SHINZA. Players progress through the game by writing comments while watching videos of [problem properties] being investigated.

name: IwoCon 2021
summary: IwoCon is a FREE digital indie game convention, played within a game! Developed by the Indie World Order to showcase recently released and upcoming indie games, IwoCon 2021 is set on a series of tropical islands with a stylized pirate theme. Come sail away with us and get ready to explore, collect, solve puzzles, and enjoy the rays of the digital sun.

name: I Will Be a Star
summary: A story about a stone that wants to become a star..! Help the main character, the stone, climb up the world tree and become a star by jumping and moving only. It is the best game to test your patience and skills!

IWL: Interstellar Wrestling League
summary: IWL: Interstellar Wrestling League came bundled with the first 6 IntelliCards.

name: IWL: Interstellar Wrestling League - 002: Character - Canned Heat
IWL: Interstellar Wrestling League - 006: Mod - Pie in the Eye
I Was Born Poor
summary: Cherubino is a boy who was born poor and he lives in village where TV is provided for free by local government. His life is truely surrounded by nothingness. But Cherubino is getting his way through poverty with the spiritual help of "Brahmana" of Brahmanas.

name: IWA Retro Adventure
summary:
A logical platform game.
Calm gameplay, but thought-provoking.
Save your brother from the clutches of an unknown monster that has kidnapped him and is now setting traps for you to hinder your search and pursuit.

name: I Wanna Be the Guy
summary:
I Wanna Be the Guy: The Movie: The Game is a 2D platform indie freeware video game created by independent developer Michael "Kayin" O'Reilly for Microsoft Windows using Multimedia Fusion 2. First released in October 2007, the game is not in active development despite being listed as a beta, though the source code for the game was released by Kayin in November 2011.

IWBTG is most famous for its difficulty. Most of the landscape is engineered specifically to kill the player character. Alongside a traditional range of recognizable dangers, such as spikes and pits, there are many less obvious threats as well, most of which are all but impossible to avoid without either previous knowledge or trial and error.

name: I Would Love to Wish You Good Morning
summary: Congratulations! You've been selected for reassignment to The Isola - a remote facility supporting vital intelligence operations at WE Inc. Your profile suggests an ideal fit for this unique position. WE looks forward to your cooperation. Best!

name: I Wanna Try
summary:
A High Difficulty Platformer you need to Try!
Complete Levels, Defeat Bosses, Find Secrets and more!
Do you have what it takes to try?

name: I Want to be a Triangle
summary: The little adventure of a Rectangle in Geoshape Prime.

name: I Wish You Rain
summary: Dark 3D (1-axis camera) platformer - beat-em-up with profound fighting system and unusual graphics.

name: I won't finish this game
summary:
"An unfinished game, something never meant to be read or posted."

Developed in response to the Going Live controversy, I won't finish this game is an extended interactive essay on suicide, art, interaction, and the bridges between them.

name: I Wanna Maker
summary: I Wanna Maker is a precision platformer with a robust level editor and online level sharing, based on I Wanna Be The Guy fangames. Create complex levels using a variety of objects, a powerful events system, and customizable visuals. Browse levels online, make playlists, and take on challenge modes!

name: I Work As An Exorcist
summary: In pure darkness, with nothing but your flashlight and conviction, it is your job to rid various places of demonic presences. The intense real-time mechanics of “Five Night’s At Freddy’s” come together with the narrative style of “Faith: The Unholy Trinity” to create a short, but rich horror experience.

name: I Want to Fly
summary: This is the story of Evie Maine, a shy girl with a difficult past. Evie is just starting her first year of university away from home. At first she's worried about fitting in, but once she sees a glider flying high above, her priorities quickly change. My name is Evie, and I want to fly.

name: IWL: Interstellar Wrestling League - 037: Mod - Bad Dentist
I Wanna Fuck My Busty Boss
summary: Experience the thrill of forbidden office romance in I Wanna Fuck My Busty Boss, a captivating visual novel where workplace drama meets intense desire. Step into the shoes of Daigo Manabe, a young professional whose life takes an unexpected turn when he develops an undeniable attraction to his alluring boss, Arisa Shinoda.

name: I Wanna Fuck My Mom's Best Friend
summary: Naoki has long harbored feelings for Shiori, his mother’s best friend, who helped raise him. Now an adult, his view of her has shifted from maternal to romantic and sexual. When his mother leaves for a work trip and asks Shiori to stay with him, the boundaries between familial familiarity and romantic tension begin to blur. Naoki wonders if his feelings may finally be reciprocated.

name: I Wanna Be the King!
summary: I Wanna Be The King! is a top-down roguelike arena shooter where you can use up to 6 allies as your weapons defeat waves of enemies. Customize your gameplay by selecting from a variety of allies and items, allowing for unique strategies and playstyles.

name: I Walk Among Zombies Vol. 0
summary: Take a step into the shoes of Mitsuki, Tokiko and Sayaka and learn a bit more about their circumstances as well as their interactions with the protagonist in these short stories that take place in around each of the games in the series.

name: I Write Games Not Tragedies
summary: An emo-inspired narrative rhythm game exploring growing pains, addiction, romance and music. Scream with Ash as he makes the transition from baby bat to elder emo, guide him through his growing pains, and help him navigate his dirtbag life through music.

name: I Will Strangle A Horse
summary:
A comedy choose-your-own-adventure game written by comedian Guy Kelly, about a man called Martin Jenkins. A man with one goal. One passion: Strangling a horse.

Does he know what a horse is? Is he aware of farms? Find out for yourself, in this 7.5k+ word game of absolute hot nonsense. I mean. Honestly. Even for Guy this is silly.

name: I Will Drown A Guy
summary:
Finally! A dark-comedy choose-your-own-adventure game written by me, actor and shenanigan-maker Emilia Copeland, about a man called Guy Kelly. A man who is apparently an actor and comedian. A man who definitely made a game about strangling a horse. A man who must now be drowned.

Can Guy Kelly even be drowned? Find out for yourself, in this 20k+ word game of delicious nonsense that will surprise absolutely no-one that knows me in person.

name: I Wanna Be the Boshy
summary: Inspired by I Wanna Be The Guy, I Wanna Be The Boshy is a "trapformer" in which a single player controls a yellow warning sign toting a pistol, whose goal is to become the "Boshy". To get there, our intrepid hero must survive an array of deadly platforming levels, where one mistake could mean death. In fact, practically every room in the game is chock-full of dodging and jumping, as well as harmless objects suddenly becoming a death trap, randomly generated events, and even a few jump-scares. As the game progresses, the player can find special treasures which unlock new features, like secret items, CD's, and new characters. Two players can also play online, with one player able to warp to the other's location if that person is further ahead.

name: I Wani Hug that Gator!
summary: I Wani Hug that Gator! Is a choice-driven narrative about teenagers struggling to find their way. Help Inco, loser highschooler extraordinaire, navigate his budding friendships (and romance!) while surviving being the only human in a dinosaur-filled school.

name: I Woke Up Next to You Again
summary:
"You’d told me,
Hey, this is a one-time thing, and I said yeah, of course -
Yet here we are.”

..who, exactly, am I waking up next to?

A romance about a more-than-one-night stand;
A psychological thriller about toxic addiction.

name: I wanna be the Yin-Yang orb
summary: This is a well-designed barrage labyrinth game. Incorporates the setting of the unlimited challenge of the I wanna series. You will be teleported to the nearest archive point when hit by the barrage. And you can reborn for unlimited times.

name: I Wanna Flip the Sky
summary: I Wanna Flip the Sky is a homebrew platformer based on physics inspired by I Wanna Be the Guy.

name: IwoCon 2
summary: IwoCon is a virtual gaming conference. Why do conventions need to be conventional? Explore gaming booths & more all done in a TPS game! Fly across the galaxy, visit space stations & drive between extraterrestrial cities & bases, all while controlling customizable avatars!

name: I Witness
summary: I Witness is a 2-player online co-op psychological horror game that follows a sibling whose curiosity leads them to investigate a neighbor suspected of being a serial killer who, unbeknownst to them, hides a disturbing desire.

name: I was here
summary: Train your ingenuity and explore the world right away from your sofa with our game-quizz "I was here" where you should guess the place by the photos.

name: I Will Be Your Eyes
summary: Two or more players work together to lead a blinded Captive out of a maze of death. Work against the clock as you avoid traps like walls of spikes, bottomless pits, and smashing hammers!

name: I Wanna Be The SuperTux 2
summary: I Wanna Be The SuperTux 2 is the sequel to I Wanna Be The SuperTux, a SuperTux mod themed around I Wanna Be The Guy.

name: IWL: Interstellar Wrestling League
summary: IWL: Interstellar Wrestling League for the HyperScan

name: I Want to be Popular!
summary:
Hey, you! Yes, you. Do you want to know what's this game about? Keep reading.

Have you ever felt the difficulties of having a public life in social media? Have you been annoyed by comments from people who hide in anonymity to say insulting things? Well, this game is for you!

name: I want 5 quadrillion yen!
summary: 5000兆円欲しい! (Gosen Cho-yen Hoshii!) is an internet meme which had been prevailed in Japan in 2017. Capture money with a goal of 5 quadrillion yen.

name: IW4x
summary: A modded PC client for Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 (2009). It adds support for dedicated servers, custom maps, and weapons.

name: I Wanna Go Home
summary: Can't stand working overtime anymore! Must find some properties to get rid of this ugly office,be aware of the mean boss,don't get caught by him!

name: I want to monopolize the older sister!
I Want Toilet!!!!!!
summary: A 2d game with "Real" physics and contains many actions and decryption elements . You can have fun in fifteen interesting stages

name: I Would Rather Have Cake
summary:
Created for O2A2: Queer Jam.

There's a girl, and a pastry chef. They talk about cakes. It's cold.

name: I Want To Cheat
summary:
I don't want my girlfriend to break up with me.....
But I want to cheat on her......
Then, I just have to 'cheat' without getting caught!!

name: I Was a Soft-boy on Tiktok...
summary: A little story about an interesting experience with a certain app

name: I Wish... Todoke, Kono Omoi
I wish I was
summary: A narrative dungeon-crawler

name: I Was Trying to Make a Game, But My Dog Was Sitting On My Lap
summary: A little bit of rambling for Manifesto Jam. games are art, and art is for everyone.

name: I wonder...
summary: I wonder when the next bus comes by...

name: I want to keep a Windy
summary: A short 2000's VIPRPG game which follows the life of a protagonist in his moments with different Windys throughout different time periods of his life(a Windy being a disposable servant whom which has one day to live upon renting).

name: I Was Wrong
summary: A gorgeous short exploration game, focused in tell the story of brilliant man, who ended up trapped inside his own mind. He needs to escape from his mind, but the only way is follow a strange female voice while he tries to remember important things by reading messages in old monitors.

name: I Was the Cat
summary:
You ever have a bad day?
Well... Today you have.

Work sucks. Your partner sucks.
And you think... maybe... life isn't worth it.

Until an angel bumps into you.

And, just like that, you have a whole new purpose in life.

Follow our unlikely heroine, as she navigates her newfound zeal for life and pursues the woman of her dreams.

name: I want cookies
summary: Very simple clicker game based on gatting cookies. If you want a simple and cheap clicker game this si your game.

name: I woke up and now I'm a knight?!
summary:
At last, the hero has arrived!

Waking up in a fantasy world on the brink of war, you'll have to rely on wits and cunning to survive, while calling on help from unlikely places!

Gather your companions and fight your way to the truth behind the vicious demon attacks before it's too late...

The key to everything is in your dreams…

name: I Will Never Give You Any Thing
summary: I WILL NEVER GIVE YOU ANY THING is an MBF21-compatible miniwad with a broken color palette.

name: I Will Become a Swordsman
summary: I Will Become a Swordsman is one of the earliest works of swordsmen of all ages. In search of a mysterious power to fight against the unknown world, the main characters seek the help of a legendary swordsman.

name: I Want to Pursue the Mean Side Character!
summary:
Beatrix is used to being misunderstood by her fellow peers.
With her sharp eyes, tall height, and ringlets, she looks like the mean villain straight from a novel.

Thus, she decided that if she was forever going to be seen as the mean bully, she might as well reside herself to the role.

However, things change when she becomes fast friends with the new commoner transfer student, to everyone’s surprise including her own.

And more weirdly, how this new transfer student can seem to understand her better than anyone else and can see her for her true self rather than the part she had been reluctantly forced to play!

name: I Was An Atomic Mutant!
summary: Assume a role of a giant monster and trash around in your room. I mean, thrash a city while being in your room. You know what I mean.

name: I Wanna Take the Time Machine
summary: Part of the "I Wanna Be" series.

name: I will Blow up the Earth Muahahahahahahaha!!!
summary: This is a game about a girl who wants to blow up the earth because she is very evil.

name: I Was in the War
summary: I Was in the War is either a philosophical look at how war can escalate out of control or an action-packed—and rather distorted—arcade game that requires quick reactions and a steady hand. It all depends on your approach.

name: I Wanna Lockpick
summary: I Wanna Lockpick tells the strange story of a girl's trip to an abstract world made of keys and doors. Or, well, I'd like it to, but really the keys and doors are the main focus here. It's a puzzle game! Assume the role of the reserved protagonist, Lily, and traverse many different abstract (and maybe beautiful?) landscapes, solving puzzles along the way. The main concept of the game is to bring colored keys to doors of the matching color, however new mechanics are introduced in each new world, with each getting progressively more unhinged and terrifying than the last.

name: I Was Dead, But…
summary: Playdate game about being a cranky ghost who wants to be left alone, made in Pulp

name: I Was Here
summary: A narrative game about two boarding school roommates that fall in and out of love with each other.

name: I Wanna Kill the Kamilia 3
summary: Featuring the all-beloved kid as his quest to kill Kamilia begins once again. As the previous editions, it's a compilation of IWBTG stages found in other fangames, only this time much higher in difficulty.

name: IWWHIIWWHITOMIROTPG: The Game!
I wanna Reach the Top
summary: In order the reach the top, you have to fall, a lot.

name: I Want To Go Home
summary: I Want To Go Home is a first-person cleaning simulator game with a horror twist. Clean the restaurant and survive to earn money and unlock characters. Play solo or with up to 3 friends and experience the story that unfolds. All content updates will be free!

name: I Want to Be a Werewolf
summary: "I Want to Be a Werewolf" is a text-based adventure where you can enjoy the detective elements of the Werewolf game and the stories of the characters.A strange room when you wake up. "werewolf game" that starts without knowing the purpose. Mystery & suspense that sees through deception.

name: I Was cursed
summary: I Was cursed is an exploration experience in which you learn to take your time and enjoy looking around you.

name: I Wanna Brother
summary: Little Timmy wants a brother! Help him manipulate their parents into making one...

name: I Will Never Forget You Because You Have Made Me the Happiest Dog on Earth
summary: Fancy dog mom simulator.

name: I Wanna Be the Co-op
summary: I Wanna Be The Co-op is a fan-made game online extension to I Wanna Be The Guy. This challenging platformer will push your skills to the utmost limits.

name: I Wanna Be the Cat
summary:
I wanna be the Cat is a challenging roguelite platformer inspired by I wanna be the Guy fangames.

Fight against famous videogame characters turned into cats and try to claim "THE CAT" as the ultimate title.

name: I Wanna Kill the Guy
summary:
A fan-game that takes directly after I Wanna Be The Guy.
Players take the role of The Guy and are being hunted down by a group called The Council.

name: I Want To Be Happy
summary: I Want To be happy is a thrilling story rich adventure tale about a young lad who wants to avenge their parents death...

name: I Want to be Alive
summary:
Immerse yourself in the cosmic atmosphere filled with many traps!
You have to go through many worlds and dangers.

name: I Want a Room in Loopy Town!
summary:
This game was a room decorating simulator with job minigames to pay for furniture.

It predates Animal Crossing by 5 years, and the game’s scenario writer was Kenji Terada, the scenario writer for Final Fantasy 1-3.

name: Iwai Keitai Kaitsuu! Tamagotchi Plus Akai
summary:
Keitai Kaitsuu Tamagotchi Plus Akai is a Japanese Tamagotchi released in July 2005. It is a themed re-release of the Keitai Kaitsuu Tamagotchi Plus featuring new characters, content, gameplay and a new base location, Makkakka Town.
Makkakka Town is a town on the Tamagotchi Planet and the home of the Akai Tamagotchi, a unique type of Tamagotchi that emit a red glow.

name: I, W.O.M.A.N.
summary: Battle dangerous robots that have been taken over by a malicious alien program. Customize your character, then fight your way to the Bridge, using power-ups and specialized weapons, to reboot the Central Computer before the berserk robots make it to the human passengers aboard the spaceship.

name: I-War
summary: I-War is a 3D virtual reality tank game. In each of the 21 levels, you must find all the data pods and make your way to the exit. Enemy tanks, turrets, and bombers stand in your way, as well as occasional traps or locked doors controlled by hidden switches. Levels are divided into simple, enclosed rooms, linearly connected by one-way teleporters.

name: Iwaihime: Extra Chapter - Musubihime
summary: Mayu Hinagata is the LCSC's dear advisor, a veritable fountain of inspiration and wisdom. But being so kind can be draining... An additional chapter by Ryukishi07.

name: I Want to Be Human
summary: A vampire girl, a hat boy and an adventure packed with tonnes of exploding body parts – go on a bloodthirsty rampage of death and destruction in a quest to become human again!

name: I Will Be There
summary: A Crazy Ex Girlfriend Adventure!

name: I Wanna Be the Creator
summary: Creation, challenge! You can be a demonic level creator, or a fearless checkpoint challenger, creating and sharing your level and bringing in more players!

name: I Wanna Take the Time-Machine 2
summary: I Wanna Take the Time-Machine 2 is a tribute to the infamous 2D platformer 'I Wanna Be the Guy', and also a sequel to I Wanna Take the Time-Machine.

name: I Wanna Eat the Lemon
summary: A short "I Wanna Be The Guy" fangame with an emphasis on "Needle" platforming and being beginner friendly.

name: I Want Watermelon
I Want To Eat Umaibo!
I Wanna Fly
summary:
"The life of the dreamer is hard - they said, dreams must be fulfilled - they said. Especially those seemingly impossible to meet. So there is nothing to wait for!

Become a fulfilled dreamer and in your own way ... start flying!

Take on one of the dozens of characters who can only dream about flying and let them enjoy the moment!"

name: I Won't Slay Dragons for You
summary:
Luke and you have been thrown into a world of fear, a maze of his own mind. Help him traverse his inner world.

He can do this.

name: I Want to Be a Girl and I Don't Know Why That's so Hard
summary:
an interactive diary entry

just felt like being a bit more creative with my ramblings this time around.

hope you all enjoy?

name: I Wanna Run the Marathon
summary: A platform game in the spirit of I Wanna be the Guy or I Wanna be the Boshy.

name: I was a Cannibal for the FBI
summary: Escape the island and avoid being eaten by the cannibals.

name: Iwatobi Penguin Rocky x Hopper 2: Tantei Monogatari
summary: Rocky Hopper has a detective with him! The definitive party game to enjoy 12 games. Story mode challenges you to play alone! Let's play party games with friends!

name: Iwatobi Penguin Rocky x Hopper
summary: Enjoy party games with the brother penguins Rocky & Hopper. Norinori Classics Super 70's dance music BGM to six! If you choose Raburabumodo, with a multi-tap controller in two pieces at a time up to four people can play!

name: I Wanna Kill Stink Terios
I Want It!
summary: I Want It! is an Xbox Live Indie Game featuring an unruly child and his mother.

name: I Want Your Heart
summary: This is a platform jumping game. You can experience happiness in it. If the game often flashes back, you can use Windows Compatibility mode to select Windows 7 to run

name: I Wanna be the Justice Guy
summary: I Wanna Be the Justice Guy is a tribute to the infamous 2D platformer 'I Wanna Be the Guy'.

name: I Wanna How Many Bottles of Coke Zero Can Badlands Chug in 3 Minutes? Watch & See!
I Wanna Lap Around
summary: A gloomy and minimal take on the needle style pioneered by Fly the Far Away, but with a higher focus on precision and density.

name: I Wanna Be The SuperTux
summary: I Wanna Be The SuperTux is a level mod for SuperTux that is inspired by I Wanna Be The Guy.

name: IWO: Bloodbath in the Bonins
summary: Iwo Jima was a critical point on the flight path of US bombers from their Saipan bases to their Japanese targets.  The island would be a refuge for malfunctioning or damaged bombers coming or going.  An obvious target for a US amphibious assault, the Japanese had reinforced the garrison and dug miles of tunnels the length and breadth of the island.  Their goal was to inflict maximum casualties on the Americans to force them to reconsider the seemingly inevitable invasion of Japan.  The resulting battle was brutal, even by the standards of the Pacific War.

name: I Want My Mommy
summary: Poor Teddy. He's had a bad dream and now he wants his mommy. How about giving him a hand? Steer him toward the magical stardust ladders. Help him avoid the nasty dream demons who try to block his path. (Mom's sending special kisses to help him out too.) Now if the little guy can just make it up a couple of big mountains, he'll get a big bear hug.

name: Iwate Mountain Dance
summary: Iwate Mountain Dance is a tough-as-nails bullet hell boss fighter. Take on unique multi-stage bosses in a grand dance of handcrafted fights, each with their own attack patterns and intense combos, as you explore the lands of Iwate and learn its history.

name: I Wanna Be the Guy: Gaiden
summary: Prequel to the infamous indie masocore title.

name: I Will: The Story of London
summary: I Will: The Story of London is an educational graphic adventure game based around full-motion video presentations on both the history of the British city of London and its various scenic points of interest.

name: I Wanna Save the Kids!
summary:
I Wanna Save the Kids (also known as IWSTK) is a freeware indie video game published by Mike "Kayin" O'Reilly, its creator, in late 2007 worldwide on his official website. It is the prequel to I Wanna Be the Guy (despite being released after it) and therefore chronologically the first game in the I Wanna Be the Guy series.

The game's mechanics are inspired by the game Lemmings: The Kid must manage to save some children, who advance regardless of the dangers, and bring them to a safe place in a kind of house. To do this he has several tools at his disposal, but most of the time he is forced to obtain these tools by overcoming IWBTG-worthy maps, complete with spikes, falling cherries and more.

name: I Want to Go to Mars
summary: A fun and exciting point & click story book adventure to Mars for kids and parents. Suitable for the young and the young at heart!

name: I Walk Among Zombies Vol. 1
summary: Yuusuke awakens in a world where zombies have overrun civilization, but finds that the zombies don't attack him. How will Yuusuke take advantage of his new situation, and what will he discover? Enjoy this twist on the classic zombie survival genre.

name: I Want to Believe
summary: I Want to Believe is a first-person action game with elements of detective work, simulation, stealth, freedom of action, and driving.

name: I Wanna Be The Crimson Needle
summary: Play as the kid as he goes through a 2D precision platforming gauntlet of 100 floors that progressively get harder in difficulty!

name: Iwakura Aria
summary: The Iwakura mansion holds a dark secret. Ichiko the new young maid joins looking for nothing but safety and security, but would soon find herself entangled with the beautiful daughter of the Iwakura household. Unravel the secrets of the Iwakura mansion in this gripping suspense visual novel.

name: I Wish Michael Phantomino Were Here
summary: You are Michael Phantomino, a little ghost who shows up wherever someone needs help solving pentamino puzzles.

name: I Wanna Commit Crimes So I Can Go to Prison Then Commit Super Crimes So I Can Go to Super Prison 64
summary: Mario is captured and sent to the jail factory, and has to find a way out. Try not to explode!

name: I Wanna Build a Robot
summary: Action-packed pixel-art old-school dungeon crawler!

name: I want to die
summary: The main character of the game, named David, goes in search of his missing daughter in a dark and ominous forest. He drives his car along a forest road, immersed in grief and despair. But on the way to his goal, his life turns into a nightmare.
